59class LoginQueryHolder : public SQLQueryHolder
60{
61 private:
62 uint32 m_accountId;
63 ObjectGuid m_guid;
64 public:
65 LoginQueryHolder(uint32 accountId, ObjectGuid guid)
66 : m_accountId(accountId), m_guid(guid) { }
67 ObjectGuid GetGuid() const { return m_guid; }
68 uint32 GetAccountId() const { return m_accountId; }
69 bool Initialize();
70};

266void WorldSession::HandleCharEnum(PreparedQueryResult result)
267{
268 WorldPackets::Character::EnumCharactersResult charEnum;
269 charEnum.Success = true;
270 charEnum.IsDeletedCharacters = false;
271
272 _legitCharacters.clear();
273
274 if (result)
275 {
276 do
277 {
278 Field* fields = result->Fetch();
279 WorldPackets::Character::EnumCharactersResult::CharacterInfo charInfo(fields);
280
281 TC_LOG_INFO("network", "Loading char guid %s from account %u.", charInfo.Guid.ToString().c_str(), GetAccountId());
282
283 if (!Player::ValidateAppearance(charInfo.Race, charInfo.Class, charInfo.Sex, charInfo.HairStyle, charInfo.HairColor, charInfo.Face, charInfo.FacialHair, charInfo.Skin))
284 {
285 TC_LOG_ERROR("entities.player.loading", "Player %s has wrong Appearance values (Hair/Skin/Color), forcing recustomize", charInfo.Guid.ToString().c_str());
286
287 if (!(charInfo.CustomizationFlag == CHAR_CUSTOMIZE_FLAG_CUSTOMIZE))
288 {
289 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_UPD_ADD_AT_LOGIN_FLAG);
290 stmt->setUInt16(0, uint16(AT_LOGIN_CUSTOMIZE));
291 stmt->setUInt64(1, charInfo.Guid.GetCounter());
292 CharacterDatabase.Execute(stmt);
293 charInfo.CustomizationFlag = CHAR_CUSTOMIZE_FLAG_CUSTOMIZE;
294 }
295 }
296
297 // Do not allow locked characters to login
298 if (!(charInfo.Flags & (CHARACTER_FLAG_LOCKED_FOR_TRANSFER | CHARACTER_FLAG_LOCKED_BY_BILLING)))
299 _legitCharacters.insert(charInfo.Guid);
300
301 if (!sWorld->HasCharacterInfo(charInfo.Guid)) // This can happen if characters are inserted into the database manually. Core hasn't loaded name data yet.
302 sWorld->AddCharacterInfo(charInfo.Guid, GetAccountId(), charInfo.Name, charInfo.Sex, charInfo.Race, charInfo.Class, charInfo.Level, false);
303
304 charEnum.Characters.emplace_back(charInfo);
305 }
306 while (result->NextRow());
307 }
308
309 SendPacket(charEnum.Write());
310}
311
312void WorldSession::HandleCharEnumOpcode(WorldPackets::Character::EnumCharacters& /*enumCharacters*/)
313{
314 // remove expired bans
315 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_EXPIRED_BANS);
316 CharacterDatabase.Execute(stmt);
317
318 /// get all the data necessary for loading all characters (along with their pets) on the account
319
320 if (sWorld->getBoolConfig(CONFIG_DECLINED_NAMES_USED))
321 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_ENUM_DECLINED_NAME);
322 else
323 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_ENUM);
324
325 stmt->setUInt8(0, PET_SAVE_AS_CURRENT);
326 stmt->setUInt32(1, GetAccountId());
327
328 _charEnumCallback.SetParam(false);
329 _charEnumCallback.SetFutureResult(CharacterDatabase.AsyncQuery(stmt));
330}

374void WorldSession::HandleCharCreateOpcode(WorldPackets::Character::CreateCharacter& charCreate)
375{
376 if (!HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_SKIP_CHECK_CHARACTER_CREATION_TEAMMASK))
377 {
378 if (uint32 mask = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_CHARACTER_CREATING_DISABLED))
379 {
380 bool disabled = false;
381
382 switch (Player::TeamIdForRace(charCreate.CreateInfo->Race))
383 {
384 case TEAM_ALLIANCE:
385 disabled = (mask & (1 << 0)) != 0;
386 break;
387 case TEAM_HORDE:
388 disabled = (mask & (1 << 1)) != 0;
389 break;
390 case TEAM_NEUTRAL:
391 disabled = (mask & (1 << 2)) != 0;
392 break;
393 }
394
395 if (disabled)
396 {
397 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_DISABLED);
398 return;
399 }
400 }
401 }
402
403 ChrClassesEntry const* classEntry = sChrClassesStore.LookupEntry(charCreate.CreateInfo->Class);
404 if (!classEntry)
405 {
406 TC_LOG_ERROR("network", "Class (%u) not found in DBC while creating new char for account (ID: %u): wrong DBC files or cheater?", charCreate.CreateInfo->Class, GetAccountId());
407 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_FAILED);
408 return;
409 }
410
411 ChrRacesEntry const* raceEntry = sChrRacesStore.LookupEntry(charCreate.CreateInfo->Race);
412 if (!raceEntry)
413 {
414 TC_LOG_ERROR("network", "Race (%u) not found in DBC while creating new char for account (ID: %u): wrong DBC files or cheater?", charCreate.CreateInfo->Race, GetAccountId());
415 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_FAILED);
416 return;
417 }
418
419 // prevent character creating Expansion race without Expansion account
420 uint8 raceExpansionRequirement = sObjectMgr->GetRaceExpansionRequirement(charCreate.CreateInfo->Race);
421 if (raceExpansionRequirement > GetExpansion())
422 {
423 TC_LOG_ERROR("network", "Expansion %u account:[%d] tried to Create character with expansion %u race (%u)", GetExpansion(), GetAccountId(), raceExpansionRequirement, charCreate.CreateInfo->Race);
424 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_EXPANSION);
425 return;
426 }
427
428 // prevent character creating Expansion class without Expansion account
429 uint8 classExpansionRequirement = sObjectMgr->GetClassExpansionRequirement(charCreate.CreateInfo->Class);
430 if (classExpansionRequirement > GetExpansion())
431 {
432 TC_LOG_ERROR("network", "Expansion %u account:[%d] tried to Create character with expansion %u class (%u)", GetExpansion(), GetAccountId(), classExpansionRequirement, charCreate.CreateInfo->Class);
433 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_EXPANSION_CLASS);
434 return;
435 }
436
437 if (!HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_SKIP_CHECK_CHARACTER_CREATION_RACEMASK))
438 {
439 uint32 raceMaskDisabled = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_CHARACTER_CREATING_DISABLED_RACEMASK);
440 if ((1 << (charCreate.CreateInfo->Race - 1)) & raceMaskDisabled)
441 {
442 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_DISABLED);
443 return;
444 }
445 }
446
447 if (!HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_SKIP_CHECK_CHARACTER_CREATION_CLASSMASK))
448 {
449 uint32 classMaskDisabled = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_CHARACTER_CREATING_DISABLED_CLASSMASK);
450 if ((1 << (charCreate.CreateInfo->Class - 1)) & classMaskDisabled)
451 {
452 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_DISABLED);
453 return;
454 }
455 }
456
457 // prevent character creating with invalid name
458 if (!normalizePlayerName(charCreate.CreateInfo->Name))
459 {
460 TC_LOG_ERROR("network", "Account:[%d] but tried to Create character with empty [name] ", GetAccountId());
461 SendCharCreate(CHAR_NAME_NO_NAME);
462 return;
463 }
464
465 // check name limitations
466 ResponseCodes res = ObjectMgr::CheckPlayerName(charCreate.CreateInfo->Name, GetSessionDbcLocale(), true);
467 if (res != CHAR_NAME_SUCCESS)
468 {
469 SendCharCreate(res);
470 return;
471 }
472
473 if (!HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_SKIP_CHECK_CHARACTER_CREATION_RESERVEDNAME) && sObjectMgr->IsReservedName(charCreate.CreateInfo->Name))
474 {
475 SendCharCreate(CHAR_NAME_RESERVED);
476 return;
477 }
478
479 if (charCreate.CreateInfo->Class == CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT && !HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_SKIP_CHECK_CHARACTER_CREATION_HEROIC_CHARACTER))
480 {
481 // speedup check for heroic class disabled case
482 if (!sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_HEROIC_CHARACTERS_PER_REALM))
483 {
484 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_UNIQUE_CLASS_LIMIT);
485 return;
486 }
487
488 // speedup check for heroic class disabled case
489 if (sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_CHARACTER_CREATING_MIN_LEVEL_FOR_HEROIC_CHARACTER) > sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_MAX_PLAYER_LEVEL))
490 {
491 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_LEVEL_REQUIREMENT);
492 return;
493 }
494 }
495
496 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_CHECK_NAME);
497 stmt->setString(0, charCreate.CreateInfo->Name);
498
499 _charCreateCallback.SetParam(charCreate.CreateInfo);
500 _charCreateCallback.SetFutureResult(CharacterDatabase.AsyncQuery(stmt));
501}
502
503void WorldSession::HandleCharCreateCallback(PreparedQueryResult result, WorldPackets::Character::CharacterCreateInfo* createInfo)
504{
505 /** This is a series of callbacks executed consecutively as a result from the database becomes available.
506 This is much more efficient than synchronous requests on packet handler, and much less DoS prone.
507 It also prevents data synchronisation errors.
508 */
509 switch (_charCreateCallback.GetStage())
510 {
511 case 0:
512 {
513 if (result)
514 {
515 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_NAME_IN_USE);
516 _charCreateCallback.Reset();
517 return;
518 }
519
520 ASSERT(_charCreateCallback.GetParam().get() == createInfo);
521
522 PreparedStatement* stmt = LoginDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(LOGIN_SEL_SUM_REALM_CHARACTERS);
523 stmt->setUInt32(0, GetAccountId());
524
525 _charCreateCallback.FreeResult();
526 _charCreateCallback.SetFutureResult(LoginDatabase.AsyncQuery(stmt));
527 _charCreateCallback.NextStage();
528 break;
529 }
530 case 1:
531 {
532 uint64 acctCharCount = 0;
533 if (result)
534 {
535 Field* fields = result->Fetch();
536 acctCharCount = uint64(fields[0].GetDouble());
537 }
538
539 if (acctCharCount >= sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_CHARACTERS_PER_ACCOUNT))
540 {
541 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_ACCOUNT_LIMIT);
542 _charCreateCallback.Reset();
543 return;
544 }
545
546 ASSERT(_charCreateCallback.GetParam().get() == createInfo);
547
548 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_SUM_CHARS);
549 stmt->setUInt32(0, GetAccountId());
550
551 _charCreateCallback.FreeResult();
552 _charCreateCallback.SetFutureResult(CharacterDatabase.AsyncQuery(stmt));
553 _charCreateCallback.NextStage();
554 break;
555 }
556 case 2:
557 {
558 if (result)
559 {
560 Field* fields = result->Fetch();
561 createInfo->CharCount = uint8(fields[0].GetUInt64()); // SQL's COUNT() returns uint64 but it will always be less than uint8.Max
562
563 if (createInfo->CharCount >= sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_CHARACTERS_PER_REALM))
564 {
565 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_SERVER_LIMIT);
566 _charCreateCallback.Reset();
567 return;
568 }
569 }
570
571 bool allowTwoSideAccounts = !sWorld->IsPvPRealm() || HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_TWO_SIDE_CHARACTER_CREATION);
572 uint32 skipCinematics = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_SKIP_CINEMATICS);
573
574 _charCreateCallback.FreeResult();
575
576 if (!allowTwoSideAccounts || skipCinematics == 1 || createInfo->Class == CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT)
577 {
578 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_CHAR_CREATE_INFO);
579 stmt->setUInt32(0, GetAccountId());
580 stmt->setUInt32(1, (skipCinematics == 1 || createInfo->Class == CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT) ? 10 : 1);
581 _charCreateCallback.SetFutureResult(CharacterDatabase.AsyncQuery(stmt));
582 _charCreateCallback.NextStage();
583 return;
584 }
585
586 _charCreateCallback.NextStage();
587 HandleCharCreateCallback(PreparedQueryResult(NULL), createInfo); // Will jump to case 3
588 break;
589 }
590 case 3:
591 {
592 bool haveSameRace = false;
593 uint32 heroicReqLevel = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_CHARACTER_CREATING_MIN_LEVEL_FOR_HEROIC_CHARACTER);
594 bool hasHeroicReqLevel = (heroicReqLevel == 0);
595 bool allowTwoSideAccounts = !sWorld->IsPvPRealm() || HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_TWO_SIDE_CHARACTER_CREATION);
596 uint32 skipCinematics = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_SKIP_CINEMATICS);
597 bool checkHeroicReqs = createInfo->Class == CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT && !HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_SKIP_CHECK_CHARACTER_CREATION_HEROIC_CHARACTER);
598
599 if (result)
600 {
601 uint32 team = Player::TeamForRace(createInfo->Race);
602 uint32 freeHeroicSlots = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_HEROIC_CHARACTERS_PER_REALM);
603
604 Field* field = result->Fetch();
605 uint8 accRace = field[1].GetUInt8();
606
607 if (checkHeroicReqs)
608 {
609 uint8 accClass = field[2].GetUInt8();
610 if (accClass == CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT)
611 {
612 if (freeHeroicSlots > 0)
613 --freeHeroicSlots;
614
615 if (freeHeroicSlots == 0)
616 {
617 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_UNIQUE_CLASS_LIMIT);
618 _charCreateCallback.Reset();
619 return;
620 }
621 }
622
623 if (!hasHeroicReqLevel)
624 {
625 uint8 accLevel = field[0].GetUInt8();
626 if (accLevel >= heroicReqLevel)
627 hasHeroicReqLevel = true;
628 }
629 }
630
631 // need to check team only for first character
632 /// @todo what to if account already has characters of both races?
633 if (!allowTwoSideAccounts)
634 {
635 uint32 accTeam = 0;
636 if (accRace > 0)
637 accTeam = Player::TeamForRace(accRace);
638
639 if (accTeam != team)
640 {
641 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_PVP_TEAMS_VIOLATION);
642 _charCreateCallback.Reset();
643 return;
644 }
645 }
646
647 // search same race for cinematic or same class if need
648 /// @todo check if cinematic already shown? (already logged in?; cinematic field)
649 while ((skipCinematics == 1 && !haveSameRace) || createInfo->Class == CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT)
650 {
651 if (!result->NextRow())
652 break;
653
654 field = result->Fetch();
655 accRace = field[1].GetUInt8();
656
657 if (!haveSameRace)
658 haveSameRace = createInfo->Race == accRace;
659
660 if (checkHeroicReqs)
661 {
662 uint8 acc_class = field[2].GetUInt8();
663 if (acc_class == CLASS_DEATH_KNIGHT)
664 {
665 if (freeHeroicSlots > 0)
666 --freeHeroicSlots;
667
668 if (freeHeroicSlots == 0)
669 {
670 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_UNIQUE_CLASS_LIMIT);
671 _charCreateCallback.Reset();
672 return;
673 }
674 }
675
676 if (!hasHeroicReqLevel)
677 {
678 uint8 acc_level = field[0].GetUInt8();
679 if (acc_level >= heroicReqLevel)
680 hasHeroicReqLevel = true;
681 }
682 }
683 }
684 }
685
686 if (checkHeroicReqs && !hasHeroicReqLevel)
687 {
688 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_LEVEL_REQUIREMENT);
689 _charCreateCallback.Reset();
690 return;
691 }
692
693 Player newChar(this);
694 newChar.GetMotionMaster()->Initialize();
695 if (!newChar.Create(sObjectMgr->GetGenerator<HighGuid::Player>().Generate(), createInfo))
696 {
697 // Player not create (race/class/etc problem?)
698 newChar.CleanupsBeforeDelete();
699
700 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_ERROR);
701 _charCreateCallback.Reset();
702 return;
703 }
704
705 if ((haveSameRace && skipCinematics == 1) || skipCinematics == 2)
706 newChar.setCinematic(1); // not show intro
707
708 newChar.SetAtLoginFlag(AT_LOGIN_FIRST); // First login
709
710 // Player created, save it now
711 newChar.SaveToDB(true);
712 createInfo->CharCount += 1;
713
714 SQLTransaction trans = LoginDatabase.BeginTransaction();
715
716 PreparedStatement* stmt = LoginDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(LOGIN_DEL_REALM_CHARACTERS_BY_REALM);
717 stmt->setUInt32(0, GetAccountId());
718 stmt->setUInt32(1, realm.Id.Realm);
719 trans->Append(stmt);
720
721 stmt = LoginDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(LOGIN_INS_REALM_CHARACTERS);
722 stmt->setUInt32(0, createInfo->CharCount);
723 stmt->setUInt32(1, GetAccountId());
724 stmt->setUInt32(2, realm.Id.Realm);
725 trans->Append(stmt);
726
727 LoginDatabase.CommitTransaction(trans);
728
729 if (createInfo->TemplateSet)
730 {
731 if (HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_USE_CHARACTER_TEMPLATES))
732 {
733 if (CharacterTemplate const* charTemplate = sObjectMgr->GetCharacterTemplate(*createInfo->TemplateSet))
734 {
735 if (charTemplate->Level != 1)
736 {
737 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_UPD_LEVEL);
738 stmt->setUInt8(0, uint8(charTemplate->Level));
739 stmt->setUInt64(1, newChar.GetGUID().GetCounter());
740 CharacterDatabase.Execute(stmt);
741 }
742 }
743 }
744 else
745 TC_LOG_WARN("cheat", "Account: %u (IP: %s) tried to use a character template without given permission. Possible cheating attempt.", GetAccountId(), GetRemoteAddress().c_str());
746 }
747
748 SendCharCreate(CHAR_CREATE_SUCCESS);
749
750 TC_LOG_INFO("entities.player.character", "Account: %u (IP: %s) Create Character: %s %s", GetAccountId(), GetRemoteAddress().c_str(), createInfo->Name.c_str(), newChar.GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
751 sScriptMgr->OnPlayerCreate(&newChar);
752 sWorld->AddCharacterInfo(newChar.GetGUID(), GetAccountId(), newChar.GetName(), newChar.GetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES_3, PLAYER_BYTES_3_OFFSET_GENDER), newChar.getRace(), newChar.getClass(), newChar.getLevel(), false);
753
754 newChar.CleanupsBeforeDelete();
755 _charCreateCallback.Reset();
756 break;
757 }
758 }
759}

761void WorldSession::HandleCharDeleteOpcode(WorldPackets::Character::CharDelete& charDelete)
762{
763 // Initiating
764 uint32 initAccountId = GetAccountId();
765
766 // can't delete loaded character
767 if (ObjectAccessor::FindPlayer(charDelete.Guid))
768 {
769 sScriptMgr->OnPlayerFailedDelete(charDelete.Guid, initAccountId);
770 return;
771 }
772
773 // is guild leader
774 if (sGuildMgr->GetGuildByLeader(charDelete.Guid))
775 {
776 sScriptMgr->OnPlayerFailedDelete(charDelete.Guid, initAccountId);
777 SendCharDelete(CHAR_DELETE_FAILED_GUILD_LEADER);
778 return;
779 }
780
781 // is arena team captain
782 if (sArenaTeamMgr->GetArenaTeamByCaptain(charDelete.Guid))
783 {
784 sScriptMgr->OnPlayerFailedDelete(charDelete.Guid, initAccountId);
785 SendCharDelete(CHAR_DELETE_FAILED_ARENA_CAPTAIN);
786 return;
787 }
788
789 uint32 accountId = 0;
790 uint8 level = 0;
791 std::string name;
792
793 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_CHARACTER_DATA_BY_GUID);
794 stmt->setUInt64(0, charDelete.Guid.GetCounter());
795
796 if (PreparedQueryResult result = CharacterDatabase.Query(stmt))
797 {
798 Field* fields = result->Fetch();
799 accountId = fields[0].GetUInt32();
800 name = fields[1].GetString();
801 level = fields[2].GetUInt8();
802 }
803
804 // prevent deleting other players' characters using cheating tools
805 if (accountId != initAccountId)
806 {
807 sScriptMgr->OnPlayerFailedDelete(charDelete.Guid, initAccountId);
808 return;
809 }
810
811 TC_LOG_INFO("entities.player.character", "Account: %u, IP: %s deleted character: %s, %s, Level: %u", accountId, GetRemoteAddress().c_str(), name.c_str(), charDelete.Guid.ToString().c_str(), level);
812
813 // To prevent hook failure, place hook before removing reference from DB
814 sScriptMgr->OnPlayerDelete(charDelete.Guid, initAccountId); // To prevent race conditioning, but as it also makes sense, we hand the accountId over for successful delete.
815 // Shouldn't interfere with character deletion though
816
817 if (sLog->ShouldLog("entities.player.dump", LOG_LEVEL_INFO)) // optimize GetPlayerDump call
818 {
819 std::string dump;
820 if (PlayerDumpWriter().GetDump(charDelete.Guid.GetCounter(), dump))
821 sLog->outCharDump(dump.c_str(), accountId, charDelete.Guid.GetCounter(), name.c_str());
822 }
823
824 sGuildFinderMgr->RemoveAllMembershipRequestsFromPlayer(charDelete.Guid);
825 sCalendarMgr->RemoveAllPlayerEventsAndInvites(charDelete.Guid);
826 Player::DeleteFromDB(charDelete.Guid, accountId);
827
828 SendCharDelete(CHAR_DELETE_SUCCESS);
829}

832{

838 }

857{

859 {
860 KickPlayer();

894void WorldSession::HandlePlayerLogin(LoginQueryHolder* holder)
895{
896 ObjectGuid playerGuid = holder->GetGuid();
897
898 Player* pCurrChar = new Player(this);
899 // for send server info and strings (config)
900 ChatHandler chH = ChatHandler(pCurrChar->GetSession());
901
902 // "GetAccountId() == db stored account id" checked in LoadFromDB (prevent login not own character using cheating tools)
903 if (!pCurrChar->LoadFromDB(playerGuid, holder))
904 {
905 SetPlayer(NULL);
906 KickPlayer(); // disconnect client, player no set to session and it will not deleted or saved at kick
907 delete pCurrChar; // delete it manually
908 delete holder; // delete all unprocessed queries
909 m_playerLoading.Clear();
910 return;
911 }
912
913 SendTutorialsData();
914
915 pCurrChar->GetMotionMaster()->Initialize();
916 pCurrChar->SendDungeonDifficulty();
917
918 WorldPackets::Character::LoginVerifyWorld loginVerifyWorld;
919 loginVerifyWorld.MapID = pCurrChar->GetMapId();
920 loginVerifyWorld.Pos = pCurrChar->GetPosition();
921 SendPacket(loginVerifyWorld.Write());
922
923 // load player specific part before send times
924 LoadAccountData(holder->GetPreparedResult(PLAYER_LOGIN_QUERY_LOAD_ACCOUNT_DATA), PER_CHARACTER_CACHE_MASK);
925
926 WorldPackets::ClientConfig::AccountDataTimes accountDataTimes;
927 accountDataTimes.PlayerGuid = playerGuid;
928 accountDataTimes.ServerTime = uint32(sWorld->GetGameTime());
929 for (uint32 i = 0; i < NUM_ACCOUNT_DATA_TYPES; ++i)
930 accountDataTimes.AccountTimes[i] = uint32(GetAccountData(AccountDataType(i))->Time);
931
932 SendPacket(accountDataTimes.Write());
933
934 SendFeatureSystemStatus();
935
936 // Send MOTD
937 {
938 WorldPackets::System::MOTD motd;
939 motd.Text = &sWorld->GetMotd();
940 SendPacket(motd.Write());
941 TC_LOG_DEBUG("network", "WORLD: Sent motd (SMSG_MOTD)");
942 }
943
944 SendSetTimeZoneInformation();
945
946 // Send PVPSeason
947 {
948 WorldPackets::Battleground::PVPSeason season;
949 season.PreviousSeason = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_ARENA_SEASON_ID) - sWorld->getBoolConfig(CONFIG_ARENA_SEASON_IN_PROGRESS);
950
951 if (sWorld->getBoolConfig(CONFIG_ARENA_SEASON_IN_PROGRESS))
952 season.CurrentSeason = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_ARENA_SEASON_ID);
953
954 SendPacket(season.Write());
955 TC_LOG_DEBUG("network", "WORLD: Sent PVPSeason");
956 }
957
958 // send server info
959 {
960 if (sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_ENABLE_SINFO_LOGIN) == 1)
961 chH.PSendSysMessage(GitRevision::GetFullVersion());
962
963 TC_LOG_DEBUG("network", "WORLD: Sent server info");
964 }
965
966 //QueryResult* result = CharacterDatabase.PQuery("SELECT guildid, rank FROM guild_member WHERE guid = '%u'", pCurrChar->GetGUIDLow());
967 if (PreparedQueryResult resultGuild = holder->GetPreparedResult(PLAYER_LOGIN_QUERY_LOAD_GUILD))
968 {
969 Field* fields = resultGuild->Fetch();
970 pCurrChar->SetInGuild(fields[0].GetUInt64());
971 pCurrChar->SetRank(fields[1].GetUInt8());
972 if (Guild* guild = sGuildMgr->GetGuildById(pCurrChar->GetGuildId()))
973 pCurrChar->SetGuildLevel(guild->GetLevel());
974 }
975 else if (pCurrChar->GetGuildId()) // clear guild related fields in case wrong data about non existed membership
976 {
977 pCurrChar->SetInGuild(UI64LIT(0));
978 pCurrChar->SetRank(0);
979 pCurrChar->SetGuildLevel(0);
980 }
981
982 //WorldPacket data(SMSG_LEARNED_DANCE_MOVES, 4+4);
983 //data << uint64(0);
984 //SendPacket(&data);
985
986 WorldPackets::Query::HotfixNotifyBlob hotfixInfo;
987 hotfixInfo.Hotfixes = sDB2Manager.GetHotfixData();
988 SendPacket(hotfixInfo.Write());
989
990 // TODO: Move this to BattlePetMgr::SendJournalLock() just to have all packets in one file
991 WorldPackets::BattlePet::BattlePetJournalLockAcquired lock;
992 SendPacket(lock.Write());
993
994 pCurrChar->SendInitialPacketsBeforeAddToMap();
995
996 //Show cinematic at the first time that player login
997 if (!pCurrChar->getCinematic())
998 {
999 pCurrChar->setCinematic(1);
1000
1001 if (ChrClassesEntry const* cEntry = sChrClassesStore.LookupEntry(pCurrChar->getClass()))
1002 {
1003 if (cEntry->CinematicSequenceID)
1004 pCurrChar->SendCinematicStart(cEntry->CinematicSequenceID);
1005 else if (ChrRacesEntry const* rEntry = sChrRacesStore.LookupEntry(pCurrChar->getRace()))
1006 pCurrChar->SendCinematicStart(rEntry->CinematicSequenceID);
1007
1008 // send new char string if not empty
1009 if (!sWorld->GetNewCharString().empty())
1010 chH.PSendSysMessage("%s", sWorld->GetNewCharString().c_str());
1011 }
1012 }
1013
1014 if (!pCurrChar->GetMap()->AddPlayerToMap(pCurrChar))
1015 {
1016 AreaTriggerStruct const* at = sObjectMgr->GetGoBackTrigger(pCurrChar->GetMapId());
1017 if (at)
1018 pCurrChar->TeleportTo(at->target_mapId, at->target_X, at->target_Y, at->target_Z, pCurrChar->GetOrientation());
1019 else
1020 pCurrChar->TeleportTo(pCurrChar->m_homebindMapId, pCurrChar->m_homebindX, pCurrChar->m_homebindY, pCurrChar->m_homebindZ, pCurrChar->GetOrientation());
1021 }
1022
1023 ObjectAccessor::AddObject(pCurrChar);
1024 //TC_LOG_DEBUG("Player %s added to Map.", pCurrChar->GetName().c_str());
1025
1026 if (pCurrChar->GetGuildId())
1027 {
1028 if (Guild* guild = sGuildMgr->GetGuildById(pCurrChar->GetGuildId()))
1029 guild->SendLoginInfo(this);
1030 else
1031 {
1032 // remove wrong guild data
1033 TC_LOG_ERROR("misc", "Player %s (%s) marked as member of not existing guild (id: " UI64FMTD "), removing guild membership for player.", pCurrChar->GetName().c_str(), pCurrChar->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), pCurrChar->GetGuildId());
1034 pCurrChar->SetInGuild(UI64LIT(0));
1035 }
1036 }
1037
1038 pCurrChar->SendInitialPacketsAfterAddToMap();
1039
1040 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_UPD_CHAR_ONLINE);
1041 stmt->setUInt64(0, pCurrChar->GetGUID().GetCounter());
1042 CharacterDatabase.Execute(stmt);
1043
1044 stmt = LoginDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(LOGIN_UPD_ACCOUNT_ONLINE);
1045 stmt->setUInt32(0, GetAccountId());
1046 LoginDatabase.Execute(stmt);
1047
1048 pCurrChar->SetInGameTime(getMSTime());
1049
1050 // announce group about member online (must be after add to player list to receive announce to self)
1051 if (Group* group = pCurrChar->GetGroup())
1052 {
1053 //pCurrChar->groupInfo.group->SendInit(this); // useless
1054 group->SendUpdate();
1055 group->ResetMaxEnchantingLevel();
1056 }
1057
1058 // friend status
1059 sSocialMgr->SendFriendStatus(pCurrChar, FRIEND_ONLINE, pCurrChar->GetGUID(), true);
1060
1061 // Place character in world (and load zone) before some object loading
1062 pCurrChar->LoadCorpse(holder->GetPreparedResult(PLAYER_LOGIN_QUERY_LOAD_CORPSE_LOCATION));
1063
1064 // setting Ghost+speed if dead
1065 if (pCurrChar->m_deathState != ALIVE)
1066 {
1067 // not blizz like, we must correctly save and load player instead...
1068 if (pCurrChar->getRace() == RACE_NIGHTELF && !pCurrChar->HasAura(20584))
1069 pCurrChar->CastSpell(pCurrChar, 20584, true, 0);// auras SPELL_AURA_INCREASE_SPEED(+speed in wisp form), SPELL_AURA_INCREASE_SWIM_SPEED(+swim speed in wisp form), SPELL_AURA_TRANSFORM (to wisp form)
1070
1071 if (!pCurrChar->HasAura(8326))
1072 pCurrChar->CastSpell(pCurrChar, 8326, true, 0); // auras SPELL_AURA_GHOST, SPELL_AURA_INCREASE_SPEED(why?), SPELL_AURA_INCREASE_SWIM_SPEED(why?)
1073
1074 pCurrChar->SetWaterWalking(true);
1075 }
1076
1077 pCurrChar->ContinueTaxiFlight();
1078
1079 // reset for all pets before pet loading
1080 if (pCurrChar->HasAtLoginFlag(AT_LOGIN_RESET_PET_TALENTS))
1081 Pet::resetTalentsForAllPetsOf(pCurrChar);
1082
1083 // Load pet if any (if player not alive and in taxi flight or another then pet will remember as temporary unsummoned)
1084 pCurrChar->LoadPet();
1085
1086 // Set FFA PvP for non GM in non-rest mode
1087 if (sWorld->IsFFAPvPRealm() && !pCurrChar->IsGameMaster() && !pCurrChar->HasFlag(PLAYER_FLAGS, PLAYER_FLAGS_RESTING))
1088 pCurrChar->SetByteFlag(UNIT_FIELD_BYTES_2, 1, UNIT_BYTE2_FLAG_FFA_PVP);
1089
1090 if (pCurrChar->HasFlag(PLAYER_FLAGS, PLAYER_FLAGS_CONTESTED_PVP))
1091 pCurrChar->SetContestedPvP();
1092
1093 // Apply at_login requests
1094 if (pCurrChar->HasAtLoginFlag(AT_LOGIN_RESET_SPELLS))
1095 {
1096 pCurrChar->ResetSpells();
1097 SendNotification(LANG_RESET_SPELLS);
1098 }
1099
1100 if (pCurrChar->HasAtLoginFlag(AT_LOGIN_RESET_TALENTS))
1101 {
1102 pCurrChar->ResetTalents(true);
1103 pCurrChar->ResetTalentSpecialization();
1104 pCurrChar->SendTalentsInfoData(); // original talents send already in to SendInitialPacketsBeforeAddToMap, resend reset state
1105 SendNotification(LANG_RESET_TALENTS);
1106 }
1107
1108 bool firstLogin = pCurrChar->HasAtLoginFlag(AT_LOGIN_FIRST);
1109 if (firstLogin)
1110 {
1111 pCurrChar->RemoveAtLoginFlag(AT_LOGIN_FIRST);
1112
1113 PlayerInfo const* info = sObjectMgr->GetPlayerInfo(pCurrChar->getRace(), pCurrChar->getClass());
1114 for (uint32 spellId : info->castSpells)
1115 pCurrChar->CastSpell(pCurrChar, spellId, true);
1116 }
1117
1118 // show time before shutdown if shutdown planned.
1119 if (sWorld->IsShuttingDown())
1120 sWorld->ShutdownMsg(true, pCurrChar);
1121
1122 if (sWorld->getBoolConfig(CONFIG_ALL_TAXI_PATHS))
1123 pCurrChar->SetTaxiCheater(true);
1124
1125 if (pCurrChar->IsGameMaster())
1126 SendNotification(LANG_GM_ON);
1127
1128 TC_LOG_INFO("entities.player.character", "Account: %u (IP: %s) Login Character: [%s] (%s) Level: %d",
1129 GetAccountId(), GetRemoteAddress().c_str(), pCurrChar->GetName().c_str(), pCurrChar->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), pCurrChar->getLevel());
1130
1131 if (!pCurrChar->IsStandState() && !pCurrChar->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_STUNNED))
1132 pCurrChar->SetStandState(UNIT_STAND_STATE_STAND);
1133
1134 m_playerLoading.Clear();
1135
1136 // Handle Login-Achievements (should be handled after loading)
1137 _player->UpdateAchievementCriteria(ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ON_LOGIN, 1);
1138
1139 sScriptMgr->OnPlayerLogin(pCurrChar, firstLogin);
1140
1141 sBattlenetServer.SendChangeToonOnlineState(GetBattlenetAccountId(), GetAccountId(), _player->GetGUID(), _player->GetName(), true);
1142
1143 delete holder;
1144}

1146void WorldSession::SendFeatureSystemStatus()
1147{
1148 WorldPackets::System::FeatureSystemStatus features;

1201void WorldSession::HandleTutorialFlag(WorldPackets::Misc::TutorialSetFlag& packet)
1202{
1203 switch (packet.Action)
1204 {
1205 case TUTORIAL_ACTION_UPDATE:
1206 {
1207 uint8 index = uint8(packet.TutorialBit >> 5);
1208 if (index >= MAX_ACCOUNT_TUTORIAL_VALUES)
1209 {
1210 TC_LOG_ERROR("network", "CMSG_TUTORIAL_FLAG received bad TutorialBit %u.", packet.TutorialBit);
1211 return;
1212 }
1213 uint32 flag = GetTutorialInt(index);
1214 flag |= (1 << (packet.TutorialBit & 0x1F));
1215 SetTutorialInt(index, flag);
1216 break;
1217 }
1218 case TUTORIAL_ACTION_CLEAR:
1219 for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_ACCOUNT_TUTORIAL_VALUES; ++i)
1220 SetTutorialInt(i, 0xFFFFFFFF);
1221 break;
1222 case TUTORIAL_ACTION_RESET:
1223 for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_ACCOUNT_TUTORIAL_VALUES; ++i)
1224 SetTutorialInt(i, 0x00000000);
1225 break;
1226 default:
1227 TC_LOG_ERROR("network", "CMSG_TUTORIAL_FLAG received unknown TutorialAction %u.", packet.Action);
1228 return;
1229 }
1230}

1263void WorldSession::HandleCharRenameOpcode(WorldPackets::Character::CharacterRenameRequest& request)
1264{
1265 if (!IsLegitCharacterForAccount(request.RenameInfo->Guid))
1266 {
1267 TC_LOG_ERROR("network", "Account %u, IP: %s tried to rename character %s, but it does not belong to their account!",
1268 GetAccountId(), GetRemoteAddress().c_str(), request.RenameInfo->Guid.ToString().c_str());
1269 KickPlayer();
1270 return;
1271 }
1272
1273 // prevent character rename to invalid name
1274 if (!normalizePlayerName(request.RenameInfo->NewName))
1275 {
1276 SendCharRename(CHAR_NAME_NO_NAME, request.RenameInfo.get());
1277 return;
1278 }
1279
1280 ResponseCodes res = ObjectMgr::CheckPlayerName(request.RenameInfo->NewName, GetSessionDbcLocale(), true);
1281 if (res != CHAR_NAME_SUCCESS)
1282 {
1283 SendCharRename(res, request.RenameInfo.get());
1284 return;
1285 }
1286
1287 // check name limitations
1288 if (!HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_SKIP_CHECK_CHARACTER_CREATION_RESERVEDNAME) && sObjectMgr->IsReservedName(request.RenameInfo->NewName))
1289 {
1290 SendCharRename(CHAR_NAME_RESERVED, request.RenameInfo.get());
1291 return;
1292 }
1293
1294 // Ensure that there is no character with the desired new name
1295 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_FREE_NAME);
1296 stmt->setUInt64(0, request.RenameInfo->Guid.GetCounter());
1297 stmt->setString(1, request.RenameInfo->NewName);
1298
1299 _charRenameCallback.SetParam(request.RenameInfo);
1300 _charRenameCallback.SetFutureResult(CharacterDatabase.AsyncQuery(stmt));
1301}

1353void WorldSession::HandleSetPlayerDeclinedNames(WorldPackets::Character::SetPlayerDeclinedNames& packet)
1354{
1355 // not accept declined names for unsupported languages
1356 std::string name;
1357 if (!ObjectMgr::GetPlayerNameByGUID(packet.Player, name))
1358 {
1359 SendSetPlayerDeclinedNamesResult(DECLINED_NAMES_RESULT_ERROR, packet.Player);
1360 return;
1361 }
1362
1363 std::wstring wname;
1364 if (!Utf8toWStr(name, wname))
1365 {
1366 SendSetPlayerDeclinedNamesResult(DECLINED_NAMES_RESULT_ERROR, packet.Player);
1367 return;
1368 }
1369
1370 if (!isCyrillicCharacter(wname[0])) // name already stored as only single alphabet using
1371 {
1372 SendSetPlayerDeclinedNamesResult(DECLINED_NAMES_RESULT_ERROR, packet.Player);
1373 return;
1374 }
1375
1376 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_DECLINED_NAME_CASES; ++i)
1377 {
1378 if (!normalizePlayerName(packet.DeclinedNames.name[i]))
1379 {
1380 SendSetPlayerDeclinedNamesResult(DECLINED_NAMES_RESULT_ERROR, packet.Player);
1381 return;
1382 }
1383 }
1384
1385 if (!ObjectMgr::CheckDeclinedNames(wname, packet.DeclinedNames))
1386 {
1387 SendSetPlayerDeclinedNamesResult(DECLINED_NAMES_RESULT_ERROR, packet.Player);
1388 return;
1389 }
1390
1391 for (int i = 0; i < MAX_DECLINED_NAME_CASES; ++i)
1392 CharacterDatabase.EscapeString(packet.DeclinedNames.name[i]);
1393
1394 SQLTransaction trans = CharacterDatabase.BeginTransaction();
1395
1396 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_DECLINED_NAME);
1397 stmt->setUInt64(0, packet.Player.GetCounter());
1398 trans->Append(stmt);
1399
1400 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_INS_CHAR_DECLINED_NAME);
1401 stmt->setUInt64(0, packet.Player.GetCounter());
1402
1403 for (uint8 i = 0; i < MAX_DECLINED_NAME_CASES; i++)
1404 stmt->setString(i + 1, packet.DeclinedNames.name[i]);
1405
1406 trans->Append(stmt);
1407
1408 CharacterDatabase.CommitTransaction(trans);
1409
1410 SendSetPlayerDeclinedNamesResult(DECLINED_NAMES_RESULT_SUCCESS, packet.Player);
1411}

1413void WorldSession::HandleAlterAppearance(WorldPackets::Character::AlterApperance& packet)
1414{
1415 BarberShopStyleEntry const* bs_hair = sBarberShopStyleStore.LookupEntry(packet.NewHairStyle);
1416 if (!bs_hair || bs_hair->Type != 0 || bs_hair->Race != _player->getRace() || bs_hair->Sex != _player->GetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES_3, PLAYER_BYTES_3_OFFSET_GENDER))
1417 return;
1418
1419 BarberShopStyleEntry const* bs_facialHair = sBarberShopStyleStore.LookupEntry(packet.NewFacialHair);
1420 if (!bs_facialHair || bs_facialHair->Type != 2 || bs_facialHair->Race != _player->getRace() || bs_facialHair->Sex != _player->GetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES_3, PLAYER_BYTES_3_OFFSET_GENDER))
1421 return;
1422
1423 BarberShopStyleEntry const* bs_skinColor = sBarberShopStyleStore.LookupEntry(packet.NewSkinColor);
1424 if (bs_skinColor && (bs_skinColor->Type != 3 || bs_skinColor->Race != _player->getRace() || bs_skinColor->Sex != _player->GetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES_3, PLAYER_BYTES_3_OFFSET_GENDER)))
1425 return;
1426
1427 BarberShopStyleEntry const* bs_face = sBarberShopStyleStore.LookupEntry(packet.NewFace);
1428 if (bs_face && (bs_face->Type != 4 || bs_face->Race != _player->getRace() || bs_face->Sex != _player->GetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES_3, PLAYER_BYTES_3_OFFSET_GENDER)))
1429 return;
1430
1431 if (!Player::ValidateAppearance(_player->getRace(), _player->getClass(), _player->GetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES_3, PLAYER_BYTES_3_OFFSET_GENDER),
1432 bs_hair->Data,
1433 packet.NewHairColor,
1434 bs_face ? bs_face->Data : _player->GetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES, PLAYER_BYTES_OFFSET_FACE_ID),
1435 bs_facialHair->Data,
1436 bs_skinColor ? bs_skinColor->Data : _player->GetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES, PLAYER_BYTES_OFFSET_SKIN_ID)))
1437 return;
1438
1439 GameObject* go = _player->FindNearestGameObjectOfType(GAMEOBJECT_TYPE_BARBER_CHAIR, 5.0f);
1440 if (!go)
1441 {
1442 SendBarberShopResult(BARBER_SHOP_RESULT_NOT_ON_CHAIR);
1443 return;
1444 }
1445
1446 if (_player->GetStandState() != UnitStandStateType(UNIT_STAND_STATE_SIT_LOW_CHAIR + go->GetGOInfo()->barberChair.chairheight))
1447 {
1448 SendBarberShopResult(BARBER_SHOP_RESULT_NOT_ON_CHAIR);
1449 return;
1450 }
1451
1452 uint32 cost = _player->GetBarberShopCost(bs_hair, packet.NewHairColor, bs_facialHair, bs_skinColor, bs_face);
1453
1454 // 0 - ok
1455 // 1, 3 - not enough money
1456 // 2 - you have to sit on barber chair
1457 if (!_player->HasEnoughMoney((uint64)cost))
1458 {
1459 SendBarberShopResult(BARBER_SHOP_RESULT_NO_MONEY);
1460 return;
1461 }
1462
1463 SendBarberShopResult(BARBER_SHOP_RESULT_SUCCESS);
1464
1465 _player->ModifyMoney(-int64(cost)); // it isn't free
1466 _player->UpdateAchievementCriteria(ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_GOLD_SPENT_AT_BARBER, cost);
1467
1468 _player->SetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES, PLAYER_BYTES_OFFSET_HAIR_STYLE_ID, uint8(bs_hair->Data));
1469 _player->SetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES, PLAYER_BYTES_OFFSET_HAIR_COLOR_ID, uint8(packet.NewHairColor));
1470 _player->SetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES_2, PLAYER_BYTES_2_OFFSET_FACIAL_STYLE, uint8(bs_facialHair->Data));
1471 if (bs_skinColor)
1472 _player->SetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES, PLAYER_BYTES_OFFSET_SKIN_ID, uint8(bs_skinColor->Data));
1473 if (bs_face)
1474 _player->SetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES, PLAYER_BYTES_OFFSET_FACE_ID, uint8(bs_face->Data));
1475
1476 _player->UpdateAchievementCriteria(ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_VISIT_BARBER_SHOP, 1);
1477
1478 _player->SetStandState(UNIT_STAND_STATE_STAND);
1479}

1520void WorldSession::HandleCharCustomizeCallback(PreparedQueryResult result, WorldPackets::Character::CharCustomizeInfo* customizeInfo)

1524 if (!result)
1525 {
1526 SendCharCustomize(CHAR_CREATE_ERROR, customizeInfo);
1527 return;

1530 Field* fields = result->Fetch();
1531

1533 uint8 plrRace = fields[1].GetUInt8();

1630void WorldSession::HandleEquipmentSetSave(WorldPackets::EquipmentSet::SaveEquipmentSet& saveEquipmentSet)
1631{
1632 if (saveEquipmentSet.Set.SetID >= MAX_EQUIPMENT_SET_INDEX) // client set slots amount
1633 return;
1634
1635 for (uint8 i = 0; i < EQUIPMENT_SLOT_END; ++i)
1636 {
1637 if (!(saveEquipmentSet.Set.IgnoreMask & (1 << i)))
1638 {
1639 ObjectGuid const& itemGuid = saveEquipmentSet.Set.Pieces[i];
1640
1641 Item* item = _player->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, i);
1642
1643 /// cheating check 1 (item equipped but sent empty guid)
1644 if (!item && !itemGuid.IsEmpty())
1645 return;
1646
1647 /// cheating check 2 (sent guid does not match equipped item)
1648 if (item && item->GetGUID() != itemGuid)
1649 return;
1650 }
1651 else
1652 saveEquipmentSet.Set.Pieces[i].Clear();
1653 }
1654
1655 saveEquipmentSet.Set.IgnoreMask &= 0x7FFFF; /// clear invalid bits (i > EQUIPMENT_SLOT_END)
1656
1657 _player->SetEquipmentSet(std::move(saveEquipmentSet.Set));
1658}

1664
1665void WorldSession::HandleUseEquipmentSet(WorldPackets::EquipmentSet::UseEquipmentSet& useEquipmentSet)
1666{
1667 ObjectGuid ignoredItemGuid;
1668 ignoredItemGuid.SetRawValue(0, 1);
1669
1670 for (uint8 i = 0; i < EQUIPMENT_SLOT_END; ++i)
1671 {
1672 TC_LOG_DEBUG("entities.player.items", "%s: ContainerSlot: %u, Slot: %u", useEquipmentSet.Items[i].Item.ToString().c_str(), useEquipmentSet.Items[i].ContainerSlot, useEquipmentSet.Items[i].Slot);
1673
1674 // check if item slot is set to "ignored" (raw value == 1), must not be unequipped then
1675 if (useEquipmentSet.Items[i].Item == ignoredItemGuid)
1676 continue;
1677
1678 // Only equip weapons in combat
1679 if (_player->IsInCombat() && i != EQUIPMENT_SLOT_MAINHAND && i != EQUIPMENT_SLOT_OFFHAND)
1680 continue;
1681
1682 Item* item = _player->GetItemByGuid(useEquipmentSet.Items[i].Item);
1683
1684 uint16 dstPos = i | (INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0 << 8);
1685
1686 if (!item)
1687 {
1688 Item* uItem = _player->GetItemByPos(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, i);
1689 if (!uItem)
1690 continue;
1691
1692 ItemPosCountVec itemPosCountVec;
1693 InventoryResult inventoryResult = _player->CanStoreItem(NULL_BAG, NULL_SLOT, itemPosCountVec, uItem, false);
1694 if (inventoryResult == EQUIP_ERR_OK)
1695 {
1696 _player->RemoveItem(INVENTORY_SLOT_BAG_0, i, true);
1697 _player->StoreItem(itemPosCountVec, uItem, true);
1698 }
1699 else
1700 _player->SendEquipError(inventoryResult, uItem, NULL);
1701 continue;
1702 }
1703
1704 if (item->GetPos() == dstPos)
1705 continue;
1706
1707 _player->SwapItem(item->GetPos(), dstPos);
1708 }
1709
1710 WorldPackets::EquipmentSet::UseEquipmentSetResult result;
1711 result.Reason = 0; // 4 - equipment swap failed - inventory is full
1712 SendPacket(result.Write());
1713}

1743 CharacterInfo const* characterInfo = sWorld->GetCharacterInfo(factionChangeInfo->Guid);
1744 if (!characterInfo)
1745 {
1746 SendCharFactionChange(CHAR_CREATE_ERROR, factionChangeInfo);
1747 return;
1748 }
1749
1750 uint8 oldRace = characterInfo->Race;
1751 uint8 playerClass = characterInfo->Class;
1752 uint8 level = characterInfo->Level;
1753
1754 if (!sObjectMgr->GetPlayerInfo(factionChangeInfo->RaceID, playerClass))
1755 {
1756 SendCharFactionChange(CHAR_CREATE_ERROR, factionChangeInfo);
1757 return;
1758 }
1759
1760 Field* fields = result->Fetch();
1761 uint16 atLoginFlags = fields[0].GetUInt16();
1762 std::string knownTitlesStr = fields[1].GetString();
1763
1764 uint16 usedLoginFlag = (factionChangeInfo->FactionChange ? AT_LOGIN_CHANGE_FACTION : AT_LOGIN_CHANGE_RACE);
1765 if (!(atLoginFlags & usedLoginFlag))
1766 {
1767 SendCharFactionChange(CHAR_CREATE_ERROR, factionChangeInfo);
1768 return;
1769 }
1770
1771 TeamId newTeamId = Player::TeamIdForRace(factionChangeInfo->RaceID);
1772 if (newTeamId == TEAM_NEUTRAL)
1773 {
1774 SendCharFactionChange(CHAR_CREATE_RESTRICTED_RACECLASS, factionChangeInfo);
1775 return;
1776 }
1777
1778 if (factionChangeInfo->FactionChange == (Player::TeamIdForRace(oldRace) == newTeamId))
1779 {
1780 SendCharFactionChange(factionChangeInfo->FactionChange ? CHAR_CREATE_CHARACTER_SWAP_FACTION : CHAR_CREATE_CHARACTER_RACE_ONLY, factionChangeInfo);
1781 return;
1782 }
1783
1784 if (!HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_SKIP_CHECK_CHARACTER_CREATION_RACEMASK))
1785 {
1786 uint32 raceMaskDisabled = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_CHARACTER_CREATING_DISABLED_RACEMASK);
1787 if ((1 << (factionChangeInfo->RaceID - 1)) & raceMaskDisabled)
1788 {
1789 SendCharFactionChange(CHAR_CREATE_ERROR, factionChangeInfo);
1790 return;
1791 }
1792 }
1793
1794 // prevent character rename to invalid name
1795 if (!normalizePlayerName(factionChangeInfo->Name))
1796 {
1797 SendCharFactionChange(CHAR_NAME_NO_NAME, factionChangeInfo);
1798 return;
1799 }
1800
1801 ResponseCodes res = ObjectMgr::CheckPlayerName(factionChangeInfo->Name, GetSessionDbcLocale(), true);
1802 if (res != CHAR_NAME_SUCCESS)
1803 {
1804 SendCharFactionChange(res, factionChangeInfo);
1805 return;
1806 }
1807

1809 if (!HasPermission(rbac::RBAC_PERM_SKIP_CHECK_CHARACTER_CREATION_RESERVEDNAME) && sObjectMgr->IsReservedName(factionChangeInfo->Name))
1810 {
1811 SendCharFactionChange(CHAR_NAME_RESERVED, factionChangeInfo);

1813 }

1815 // character with this name already exist
1816 ObjectGuid newGuid = ObjectMgr::GetPlayerGUIDByName(factionChangeInfo->Name);
1817 if (!newGuid.IsEmpty())
1818 {

1822 return;
1823 }
1824 }

1826 if (sArenaTeamMgr->GetArenaTeamByCaptain(factionChangeInfo->Guid))
1827 {

1829 return;

2192 return;
2193 }

2209 uint32 index = maskID / 32;
2210 uint32 old_flag = 1 << (maskID % 32);
2211 uint32 new_flag = 1 << (atitleInfo->MaskID % 32);
2212 if (knownTitles[index] & old_flag)
2213 {
2214 knownTitles[index] &= ~old_flag;
2215 // use index of the new title
2216 knownTitles[atitleInfo->MaskID / 32] |= new_flag;
2217 }
2218 }
2219 else
2220 {
2221 uint32 maskID = atitleInfo->MaskID;
2222 uint32 index = maskID / 32;
2223 uint32 old_flag = 1 << (maskID % 32);
2224 uint32 new_flag = 1 << (htitleInfo->MaskID % 32);
2225 if (knownTitles[index] & old_flag)
2226 {
2227 knownTitles[index] &= ~old_flag;
2228 // use index of the new title
2229 knownTitles[htitleInfo->MaskID / 32] |= new_flag;
2230 }
2231 }
2232
2233 std::ostringstream ss;
2234 for (uint32 index = 0; index < ktcount; ++index)
2235 ss << knownTitles[index] << ' ';
2236
2237 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_UPD_CHAR_TITLES_FACTION_CHANGE);
2238 stmt->setString(0, ss.str());
2239 stmt->setUInt64(1, lowGuid);
2240 trans->Append(stmt);
2241
2242 // unset any currently chosen title
2243 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_RES_CHAR_TITLES_FACTION_CHANGE);
2244 stmt->setUInt64(0, lowGuid);
2245 trans->Append(stmt);
2246 }
2247 }
2248 }
2249 }
2250
2251 CharacterDatabase.CommitTransaction(trans);
2252
2253 TC_LOG_DEBUG("entities.player", "%s (IP: %s) changed race from %u to %u", GetPlayerInfo().c_str(), GetRemoteAddress().c_str(), oldRace, factionChangeInfo->RaceID);
2254
2255 SendCharFactionChange(RESPONSE_SUCCESS, factionChangeInfo);
2256}

2327 _undeleteCooldownStatusCallback.FreeResult();
2328 _undeleteCooldownStatusCallback.SetFutureResult(LoginDatabase.AsyncQuery(stmt));
2329 _undeleteCooldownStatusCallback.NextStage();
2330 break;
2331 }
2332 case 1:
2333 {
2334 uint32 cooldown = 0;
2335 uint32 maxCooldown = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_FEATURE_SYSTEM_CHARACTER_UNDELETE_COOLDOWN);
2336 if (result)
2337 {
2338 uint32 lastUndelete = result->Fetch()[0].GetUInt32();
2339 uint32 now = uint32(time(nullptr));
2340 if (lastUndelete + maxCooldown > now)
2341 cooldown = std::max<uint32>(0, lastUndelete + maxCooldown - now);
2342 }
2343
2344 SendUndeleteCooldownStatusResponse(cooldown, maxCooldown);
2345 _undeleteCooldownStatusCallback.Reset();
2346 break;
2347 }
2348 }
2349
2350}

2352void WorldSession::HandleCharUndeleteOpcode(WorldPackets::Character::UndeleteCharacter& undeleteInfo)
2353{
2354 if (!sWorld->getBoolConfig(CONFIG_FEATURE_SYSTEM_CHARACTER_UNDELETE_ENABLED))
2355 {

2357 return;
2358 }

2361 stmt->setUInt32(0, GetBattlenetAccountId());

2364 _charUndeleteCallback.SetFutureResult(LoginDatabase.AsyncQuery(stmt));
2365 _charUndeleteCallback.NextStage();

2367
2368void WorldSession::HandleCharUndeleteCallback(PreparedQueryResult result, WorldPackets::Character::CharacterUndeleteInfo* undeleteInfo)
2369{
2370 /** This is a series of callbacks executed consecutively as a result from the database becomes available.
2371 * This is much more efficient than synchronous requests on packet handler.
2372 * It also prevents data synchronisation errors.
2373 */
2374
2375 ASSERT(_charUndeleteCallback.GetParam().get() == undeleteInfo);
2376
2377 switch (_charUndeleteCallback.GetStage())
2378 {
2379 case 1:
2380 {
2381 if (result)
2382 {
2383 uint32 lastUndelete = result->Fetch()[0].GetUInt32();
2384 uint32 maxCooldown = sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_FEATURE_SYSTEM_CHARACTER_UNDELETE_COOLDOWN);
2385 if (lastUndelete && (lastUndelete + maxCooldown > time(nullptr)))
2386 {
2387 SendUndeleteCharacterResponse(CHARACTER_UNDELETE_RESULT_ERROR_COOLDOWN, undeleteInfo);
2388 _charUndeleteCallback.Reset();
2389 return;
2390 }
2391 }
2392
2393 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_CHAR_DEL_INFO_BY_GUID);
2394 stmt->setUInt64(0, undeleteInfo->CharacterGuid.GetCounter());
2395
2396 _charUndeleteCallback.FreeResult();
2397 _charUndeleteCallback.SetFutureResult(CharacterDatabase.AsyncQuery(stmt));
2398 _charUndeleteCallback.NextStage();
2399 break;
2400 }
2401 case 2:
2402 {
2403 if (!result)
2404 {
2405 SendUndeleteCharacterResponse(CHARACTER_UNDELETE_RESULT_ERROR_CHAR_CREATE, undeleteInfo);
2406 _charUndeleteCallback.Reset();
2407 return;
2408 }
2409
2410 Field* fields = result->Fetch();
2411 undeleteInfo->Name = fields[1].GetString();
2412 uint32 account = fields[2].GetUInt32();
2413
2414 if (account != GetAccountId())
2415 {
2416 SendUndeleteCharacterResponse(CHARACTER_UNDELETE_RESULT_ERROR_UNKNOWN, undeleteInfo);
2417 _charUndeleteCallback.Reset();
2418 return;
2419 }
2420
2421 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_CHECK_NAME);
2422 stmt->setString(0, undeleteInfo->Name);
2423
2424 _charUndeleteCallback.FreeResult();
2425 _charUndeleteCallback.SetFutureResult(CharacterDatabase.AsyncQuery(stmt));
2426 _charUndeleteCallback.NextStage();
2427 break;
2428 }
2429 case 3:
2430 {
2431 if (result)
2432 {
2433 SendUndeleteCharacterResponse(CHARACTER_UNDELETE_RESULT_ERROR_NAME_TAKEN_BY_THIS_ACCOUNT, undeleteInfo);
2434 _charUndeleteCallback.Reset();
2435 return;
2436 }
2437
2438 /// @todo: add more safety checks
2439 /// * max char count per account
2440 /// * max heroic char count
2441 /// * team violation
2442
2443 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_SEL_SUM_CHARS);
2444 stmt->setUInt32(0, GetAccountId());
2445
2446 _charUndeleteCallback.FreeResult();
2447 _charUndeleteCallback.SetFutureResult(CharacterDatabase.AsyncQuery(stmt));
2448 _charUndeleteCallback.NextStage();
2449 break;
2450 }
2451 case 4:
2452 {
2453 if (result)
2454 {
2455 Field* fields = result->Fetch();
2456
2457 if (fields[0].GetUInt64() >= sWorld->getIntConfig(CONFIG_CHARACTERS_PER_REALM)) // SQL's COUNT() returns uint64 but it will always be less than uint8.Max
2458 {
2459 SendUndeleteCharacterResponse(CHARACTER_UNDELETE_RESULT_ERROR_CHAR_CREATE, undeleteInfo);
2460 _charUndeleteCallback.Reset();
2461 return;
2462 }
2463 }
2464
2465 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_UPD_RESTORE_DELETE_INFO);
2466 stmt->setString(0, undeleteInfo->Name);
2467 stmt->setUInt32(1, GetAccountId());
2468 stmt->setUInt64(2, undeleteInfo->CharacterGuid.GetCounter());
2469 CharacterDatabase.Execute(stmt);
2470
2471 stmt = LoginDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(LOGIN_UPD_LAST_CHAR_UNDELETE);
2472 stmt->setUInt32(0, GetBattlenetAccountId());
2473 LoginDatabase.Execute(stmt);
2474
2475 sWorld->UpdateCharacterInfoDeleted(undeleteInfo->CharacterGuid, false, &undeleteInfo->Name);
2476
2477 SendUndeleteCharacterResponse(CHARACTER_UNDELETE_RESULT_OK, undeleteInfo);
2478 _charUndeleteCallback.Reset();
2479 break;
2480 }
2481 }
2482}
